              "plain_text": "The current KT approaches either model knowledge for different concepts separately or fail at capturing longer-term dependencies in an historical sequence of questions. To address this issue, the authors propose Bayesian Cognitive-Aware Key-Value Memory Networks, a model that combines multiple popular KT architectures (DKVMN, LSTM and Bayesian theory). ",
