    {
      "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-802c-998b-eb9ae4c6baa0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In essence, longer-term dependencies are captured by introducing an LSTM layer to DKVMN. In addition, an embedding layer is used top infer question difficulty on final predictions and Bayesian theory for better parameter interpretation. Testing on different 3-real world datasets shows that the approach achieve SotA performance. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
